flowchart LR
    subgraph trigger[Trigger]
        Event[Event Received]
    end

    subgraph detect[Detection]
        Check{Work Needed?}
    end

    subgraph action[Action]
        Skip[Skip]
        Execute[Execute]
    end

    Event --> Check
    Check -->|No| Skip
    Check -->|Yes| Execute

